		<title>The Materiality of Media</title>
		<link>http://blog.commarts.wisc.edu/2011/09/08/the-materiality-of-media/</link>
		<comments>http://blog.commarts.wisc.edu/2011/09/08/the-materiality-of-media/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Thu, 08 Sep 2011 14:37:20 +0000</pubDate>
