		<title>What We Talk About When We Talk About Net Neutrality</title>
		<link>http://blog.commarts.wisc.edu/2010/10/27/what-we-talk-about-when-we-talk-about-net-neutrality/</link>
		<comments>http://blog.commarts.wisc.edu/2010/10/27/what-we-talk-about-when-we-talk-about-net-neutrality/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Wed, 27 Oct 2010 18:04:00 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator>Danny Kimball</dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Industry]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Internet]]></category>
