		<title>What Google&#8217;s Experimental Fiber Network Means for Broadband</title>
		<link>http://blog.commarts.wisc.edu/2010/02/16/what-googles-experimental-fiber-network-means-for-broadband/</link>
		<comments>http://blog.commarts.wisc.edu/2010/02/16/what-googles-experimental-fiber-network-means-for-broadband/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Tue, 16 Feb 2010 14:29:23 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator>Danny Kimball</dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Internet]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Perspectives]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[broadband]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[digital media]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[FCC]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Google]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[internet]]></category>
